Whereas, you know, you find, "I'm paying attention."

00:01:38.700 --> 00:01:41.740
And, okay, so this is, uh, the device.

00:01:41.900 --> 00:01:43.900
And, if, if I were paying, paying attention,

00:01:43.900 --> 00:01:45.900
I'm not being distracted by the camera or anything,

00:01:46.100 --> 00:01:48.680
then I can do this, focus, parallel,

00:01:49.060 --> 00:01:51.760
and tug, tug, tug, it does go up. [funicular tugging noise]

