Brady: Hehehe, All right, what's going on here?

00:01:53.180 --> 00:01:54.740
Tadashi: What we are doing,

00:01:54.740 --> 00:01:56.980
suppose that, keeping the strings parallel,

00:01:57.440 --> 00:02:00.120
I tug on the left one,

00:02:00.460 --> 00:02:03.580
whereas, I let go of the right one.

00:02:03.580 --> 00:02:05.980
And when they do this initially,  you see...

00:02:06.840 --> 00:02:08.280
To exaggerate a little,

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:11.940
this clip turns a little, like this.

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:17.460
