00:02:17.460 --> 00:02:20.020
only lightly. Whereas the right one is

00:02:20.220 --> 00:02:22.460
entangled with the clip

00:02:22.940 --> 00:02:25.400
so this produces more friction

00:02:25.620 --> 00:02:26.360
