00:02:40.900 --> 00:02:45.980
but because the right friction is the static and entangled friction

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:49.180
and the left one is the sliding and free friction

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:53.140
and this push up is stronger than this pull down

00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:55.600
that's why in this rope it goes up

00:02:56.260 --> 00:02:59.100
and similarly when I pull the right one and left one

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:00.880
Now it twists like this

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:04.760
